      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Rise above the Mud",
        "Client": "Determined Hunter",
        "Description": "Aaaargh! I was SO close! *sigh*\r\nRight as I was about to land the final\r\nblow on a Barroth, my feet got stuck\r\nin some mud! Not only did it proceed\r\nto stomp the crap out of me, but then\r\nit got away! Once I\u0027m better\u2014*ouch*\r\nI\u0027m gonna go and finish what I started!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Barroth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Sus \u00E0 la gadoue",
        "Client": "Chasseur d\u00E9termin\u00E9",
        "Description": "Arg ! J\u0027y \u00E9tais presque ! *soupir*\r\nJ\u0027\u00E9tais sur le point d\u0027achever le\r\nBarroth quand je me suis retrouv\u00E9\r\ncoinc\u00E9 dans la boue ! Forc\u00E9ment,\r\nil m\u0027a \u00E9crabouill\u00E9 et il a fini\r\npar s\u0027enfuir ! Une fois que j\u0027irai\r\n*a\u00EFe* mieux, je lui ferai sa f\u00EAte !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Barroth",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Rialzati dal fango",
        "Client": "Cacciatore determinato",
        "Description": "Aaargh, c\u0027ero quasi! Stavo per\r\ndare il colpo di grazia a un\r\nBarroth, ma mi si \u00E8 incastrato\r\nil piede nel fango. Cos\u00EC me ne\r\nha date di santa ragione ed \u00E8\r\nfuggito. Quando star\u00F2 meglio,\r\nfinir\u00F2 ci\u00F2 che ho iniziato.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Barroth",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Raus aus dem Schlamm",
        "Client": "Entschlossener J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "Aaaargh! Ich war SO nah dran! *seufz*\r\nIch wollte einem Barroth gerade den\r\nGnadensto\u00DF versetzen, bin aber im\r\nSchlamm stecken geblieben! Er hat\r\nmich niedergetrampelt und ist auf\r\nund davon! Wenn ich wieder fit bin--\r\nautsch... bringe ich das zu Ende!",
